 <body>
  <h1>
   mouse_button
  </h1>
  This
  <b>
   read only
  </b>
  variable returns the mouse button that is currently being pressed (currently, as in, this step) and can return any of the special
  <a href="Mouse_Input.htm">
   mouse constants
  </a>
  except
  <span>
   mb_any
  </span>
  .
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">mouse_button;
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Game_Input/Mouse_Input/mouse_check_button.htm">
 Mouse Button Constant
</a>
(except mb_any)
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   <b>
    Example:
   </b>
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if mouse_button = mb_left
{
    x -= 1;
}
</code></pre>
  This moves the current instance left if the left mouse button is down.
 </body>
</html>